videoSnippet.title: The Gift of Chess Summer Charity Stream! - lichess.org
videoSnippet.description:
DONATE HERE! https://www.gofundme.com/f/agadmator-hosts-the-gift-of-chess-charity-stream
Tournament here https://lichess.org/tournament/fpucEvKW

Join us on Saturday, August 5th from 19:00 - 21:00 CET as Agamador hosts our The Gift of Chess Summer Charity Stream! Hear from our Global Ambassadors on their distribution efforts and hear how you can help us continue to spread The Gift of Chess across Africa and beyond.

The Gift of Chess Summer Charity Stream. Help us raise money to give The Gift of Chess to more countries. We currently have 50,000 chess sets in Africa with the hopes of reaching each country with 1,000 chess sets.

It costs approximately 5,000 to ship, clear customs and distribute 1,000 chess sets into a new country. Chess is a game with incredible societal benefit but unfortunately there is lack of chess sets in many countries globally. Help us expand opportunities by getting more chess sets into communities across the world.
